{"tid":2416983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英格蘭所有成人7月底前打武肺疫苗，即將解封","createTime":"2021-02-21T13:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T14:17:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d7bf2b6718751a66dd4f98324c9628cbc6836783","tid":2416983,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/iPrIJCBcL6YZfyPXEPaZEQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/97817750-741d-11eb-b577-6f594953fc78\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FiPrIJCBcL6YZfyPXEPaZEQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2F97817750-741d-11eb-b577-6f594953fc78&h=2886ab73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜訂下新的武肺疫苗接種目標，承諾今年7月底前讓國內所有成年人接種首劑疫苗，比政府早前訂立的9月目標為早。他指加快接種疫苗有助放寬部分防疫措施，周日（21日）將與內閣討論放寬英格蘭的封城措施，料周一（22日）向國會交代解封路線圖。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，本月15日已經完成為4類高風險人士，包括70歲以上長者、前線醫護人員等接種疫苗。根據新計劃，當局4月15日前為50歲以上成年人及有長期病患人士接種，期望3個月後所有成年人接種首劑疫苗。英國超過1,700萬人已經接種首劑疫苗，其中60萬人完成接種兩劑。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜表示，疫苗計劃可以更快保護高風險人士，強調放寬防疫措施需要審慎及分階段進行。首相府消息指，政府可能把限聚令人數放寬至6人，下月8日學校可復課，但店舖關閉及限制戶外社交活動等措施維持至4月。"},{"pid":"31d1527d1ac64ee88d309cbe2434c355ecf77893","tid":2416983,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf49aaef0ac41fea96afd3802f08d6ce6714fe5","tid":2416983,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"5號仔<br />\n6號仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbc77930af6fbb3886cfcce0893965596c5c5f5","tid":2416983,"uid":45003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"將疫苗放入供水系統啦 重慢慢打"},{"pid":"70f69e705798020a455219f4f8b15606443cdce9","tid":2416983,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"所有？咁癲？"}]}